WHAT BEAR SAYS,

31:53.041 --> 31:55.522
I'LL DO EVERYTHING IN MY
POWER TO PROTECT THIS LAND.

31:56.827 --> 31:57.698
-THANK YOU.

31:59.656 --> 32:01.615
-BEAR, MAN,
THAT WAS AMAZING!

32:01.745 --> 32:03.008
-YEAH, HOW DID YOU DO IT?

32:03.138 --> 32:05.053
-I DIDN'T DO
ANYTHING.

32:05.880 --> 32:07.316
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT I
WANT TO DO, THOUGH.

32:07.447 --> 32:08.752
