IS GETTING TO YOU.

40:39.088 --> 40:40.307
COME ON. ONE HERE.

40:40.438 --> 40:41.743
-NO, MITCH,
I'M NOT IN THE MOOD.

40:41.874 --> 40:43.266
-COME ON, SHOW ME...
ONE JAB, ONE JAB.

40:43.397 --> 40:44.224
COME ON, ONE JAB,
RIGHT THERE, COME ON!

40:44.354 --> 40:46.400
-NO.
-ONE QUICK JAB.

40:48.402 --> 40:49.185
OOH.

40:49.316 --> 40:51.971
-OOH. WHAT HAPPENED?

40:52.101 --> 40:54.582
-ONE...QUICK JAB.

40:55.278 --> 40:56.062
-NOT AGAIN?

40:56.192 --> 40:57.672
-I COULDN'T HELP MYSELF.

40:57.803 --> 41:00.109
