FROM GETTING SAND

41:19.259 --> 41:20.173
IN THIS CAST.

41:20.303 --> 41:21.870
-YOU'RE BACK ON THE BEACH.

41:22.001 --> 41:23.393
LORD HELP ME,
I'M BACK ON THE BEACH.

41:23.524 --> 41:24.569
-I'M SO SORRY.

41:25.526 --> 41:26.745
-SAY, LISTEN,
DID YOU EVER FIGURE OUT

41:26.875 --> 41:28.268
WHO THOSE DUNE BUGGY
DRIVERS WERE?

41:28.398 --> 41:29.443
